    <img src="~/Images/InnsideBanner/Learning_at_MLSI/Clubs-and-Extra-Curricular-Activities.jpg" alt="" class="img-fluid" />
    <div class="container">
        <div class="Topic">
            <a href="#" class="scrollto">
                <p>
                    We have an initiative at MLSI that works towards the holistic development of the child, so our clubs are focused on exposing students to new experiences. 
                </p>
            </a>
